text: Lukman Iqbal Meriwala (born 11 December 1991) is an Indian cricketer who plays for Baroda in domestic cricket. He is a left-arm fast-medium bowler who was the leading wicket-taker of the 2013/14 Syed Mushtaq Ali Trophy which Baroda won. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Baroda cricketers
